    "title": "Verified publisher in the snapstore",
    "body": "Hello, currently the official bitcoin core snapcraft publisher account is not verified.\r\nOther accounts on snapcraft.io are verified ([Spotify](https://snapcraft.io/spotify), [JetBrains](https://snapcraft.io/intellij-idea-ultimate), etc). These accounts have a little badge in the upper corner.\r\n\r\nI think it is necessary to apply for a verification because releasing an app in the snapstore is easy and fakes could be easily published, most people aren't verifying their snaps at least it isn't a thing there.\r\n\r\nCould someone (preferable the person who is responsible for the snap) apply for it?\r\nI haven't seen a form to do this but I think the [forum](https://forum.snapcraft.io/categories) is the correct place.\r\n\r\nAlso a good way would be by contacting their [twitter](https://twitter.com/snapcraftio) with the Bitcoin Core Account because this indicates authenticity.",
